lead_paragraph: Leroy Sane has found his feet in England and is ready for an extended run in the Manchester City side after the German forward scored his first goal for the club on Sunday, team mate Raheem Sterling has said.

headline.print_headline: Sterling Expects Sane to Kick on After Netting First Goal
headline.main: Sterling Expects Sane to Kick on After Netting First Goal
